							<h3>Applied Bank Platinum Zero® Secured Visa®</h3>
							<ul>
								<li>Bad Credit is no problem! </li>
								<li>0% APR for life. Simple flat monthly fee.</li>
								<li>Build credit with monthly bureau reporting.</li>
							</ul>	
						</div>
						<div class="compareTopCardRowC3"><%= link_to("SIGN UP", {:controller => 'partners', :action => 'go', :id => '36', :page=>@page}, :class => "compareTopCardApply", :target => "_blank") %></div>
					</div>

					<div class="compareTopCardRow">
						<div class="compareTopCardRowC1"><%= link_to(image_tag("prepaid/42_ACE_2010_Gunmetal_Visa_flat.jpg"), {:controller => 'partners', :action => 'go', :id => '177', :page=>@page}, :target => "_blank") %></div>
						<div class="compareTopCardRowC2">
							<h3>ACE Elite™ Visa® Prepaid Card</h3>
							<ul>
								<li>No credit check! Just sign up.</li>
								<li>Free cash withdrawals at ACE with direct deposit.</li>
								<li>Free $10 overspend cushion on purchases.</li>
							</ul>	
						</div>
						<div class="compareTopCardRowC3"><%= link_to("SIGN UP", {:controller => 'partners', :action => 'go', :id => '177', :page=>@page}, :class => "compareTopCardApply", :target => "_blank") %></div>
					</div>
					<div class="compareTopCardRowLast">
						<div class="compareTopCardRowC1"><%= link_to(image_tag("prepaid/upside-visa-prepaid-card.gif"), {:controller => 'partners', :action => 'go', :id => '80', :page=>@page}, :target => "_blank") %></div>
						<div class="compareTopCardRowC2">
							<h3>UPside Visa® Prepaid Card</h3>
							<ul>
								<li>Low $0.99 fee when you load $500/month.</li>
								<li>ATM withdrawal fees are lower than average.</li>
								<li>Only prepaid card with cash back rewards.</li>
							</ul>	
						</div>
						<div class="compareTopCardRowC3"><%= link_to("SIGN UP", {:controller => 'partners', :action => 'go', :id => '80', :page=>@page}, :class => "compareTopCardApply", :target => "_blank") %></div>
					</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			
			<div class="lpCardDetails">
				<div class="cardBestForBanner">Is <b>First Progress</b> Best for Me?</div>
				<div class="cardDetailsTable lpBadCredit">
					<div class="lpCardDetailsRow">
						<h3>The <%= link_to("First Progress Secured", {:controller => 'partners', :action => 'go', :id => '37', :page=>@page}, :target => "_blank") %> is our most popular card and,</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Paying off your balances means no interest.</li>
							<li>Responsible usage can improve your credit score.</li>
						</ul>	
						<p>However, you might prefer a different card...</p>
