					<div class="lpCardDetailsRow">
						<h3><%= image_tag("lp/CompareDesign/circlecross-icon.png", :size => "10x10") %> Do you carry credit card balances?</h3>
						<p>The <%= link_to("Applied Bank Platinum", {:controller => 'partners', :action => 'go', :id => '36', :page=>@page}, :target => "_blank") %> is a top choice with a 0% APR for life and credit building. It reports to the major bureaus.</p>
						<p><%= link_to("Sign Up Applied Bank Platinum >>", {:controller => 'partners', :action => 'go', :id => '36', :page=>@page}, :target => "_blank") %></p>
					</div>
					<div class="lpCardDetailsRowLast">
						<h3><%= image_tag("lp/CompareDesign/circlecross-icon.png", :size => "10x10") %> Do you prefer a prepaid card?</h3>
						<p>The <%= link_to("ACE Elite", {:controller => 'partners', :action => 'go', :id => '177', :page=>@page}, :target => "_blank") %> is a popular prepaid card with our users because it has free cash withdrawals at ACE stores. Our users also like the <%= link_to("UPside Visa Prepaid", {:controller => 'partners', :action => 'go', :id => '80', :page=>@page}, :target => "_blank") %> for its low monthly fee and cashback rewards program.</p>
						<p><%= link_to("Sign up for the ACE Elite Card >>", {:controller => 'partners', :action => 'go', :id => '177', :page=>@page}, :target => "_blank") %></p>
						<p><%= link_to("Sign up for the UPside Prepaid Card >>", {:controller => 'partners', :action => 'go', :id => '80', :page=>@page}, :target => "_blank") %></p>
